- Oh, it's wonderful.
Everything is wonderful.

06:53.415 --> 06:54.926
- Do you remember
our first date?

06:55.026 --> 06:56.959
You took me to that little
topless bar on 8th

06:57.059 --> 06:58.839
and then we went dancing?

06:58.939 --> 07:00.911
- Yeah.
How come we don't dance anymore?

07:01.011 --> 07:04.133
- I was waiting all night
for you to kiss me.

07:04.233 --> 07:06.473
Finally I couldn't wait
any longer,
so I just grabbed you.

07:06.573 --> 07:08.952
- Even back then,
when you wanted something,
you went right after it.

07:10.563 --> 07:12.995
- You like that about me, right?

07:13.095 --> 07:14.837
- Sure.
Why?

07:14.937 --> 07:16.947
- This is why.

07:22.034 --> 07:24.313
May I please have
everyone's attention?

07:24.413 --> 07:26.331
- Vanessa, what are you doing?

07:27.904 --> 07:31.640
- Tonight marks four years,
four days, and one hour

07:31.740 --> 07:35.692
since Daniel and I fell
in love at first sight.

07:36.958 --> 07:39.582
Aww, he's shy.
It's one of the things
I love about him.

07:39.682 --> 07:43.380
Anyway, he's always teasing me
about being larger than life,

07:43.480 --> 07:47.753
so when he told me we were
coming here to this
amazing restaurant,

07:47.853 --> 07:50.078
I thought,
"What better place than this?"

08:33.277 --> 08:38.010
Daniel,
light of my life,

08:38.110 --> 08:39.429
will you marry me?

08:51.001 --> 08:52.919
- Daniel.

08:53.878 --> 08:55.159
- Sit down, okay?

08:55.259 --> 08:58.152
- Once you say yes
and put the ring on my finger.

09:01.398 --> 09:03.599
- I don't wanna answer you
here like this.

09:03.699 --> 09:06.477
- Then just give me
a temporary yes
and we'll talk about it later.

09:13.712 --> 09:15.492
- Say yes.

09:19.467 --> 09:20.940
- No.

09:22.728 --> 09:24.163
- That's a million views
on YouTube.

09:24.263 --> 09:26.181
- Lewis, put the phone away.

09:31.398 --> 09:33.317
- Vanessa...

09:34.889 --> 09:36.746
Wait, hang on.
I'll get the check.

09:36.846 --> 09:39.662
- Get the check?
Four years, Daniel.

09:39.762 --> 09:40.966
We've been together four years.

09:41.066 --> 09:42.083
What have you been doing
all this time

09:42.179 --> 09:43.613
if you were just gonna say no?

09:43.713 --> 09:45.647
- I didn't know, I was
- I'm a woman, Daniel.

09:45.747 --> 09:48.639
I'm a 28-year-old woman.
This is what we do.

09:48.739 --> 09:50.964
We diet, we get married,
we have kids,
and we diet again.

09:51.655 --> 09:53.665
Look at what I did
for you tonight.

09:53.765 --> 09:55.683
Look how much I love you.

09:58.023 --> 09:59.941
Is a yes too much?

10:11.527 --> 10:14.343
- Everyone, my name
is Vanessa Sanchez.

10:14.443 --> 10:17.604
I can cook,
I have my own business,
and as of this moment,

10:17.704 --> 10:20.942
I am officially single.

10:21.042 --> 10:22.476
- Ooh.

10:22.576 --> 10:24.126
- Google me
if you're interested.

10:26.106 --> 10:28.423
- Good for her.
- I'm gonna Google her.

10:38.114 --> 10:39.510
I keep calling,
but she's not answering.

10:39.610 --> 10:41.006
- Of course not, bro.

10:41.106 --> 10:42.963
I mean, you dropped
a nuclear bomb on her head.

10:43.063 --> 10:44.919
I mean, don't get me wrong.
I'm really proud of you.

10:45.019 --> 10:47.858
I'd never think
of having the balls
to crush her like that.

10:48.856 --> 10:49.983
- How soon can you pick me up?

10:50.083 --> 10:52.439
- Uh, Daniel, uh,

10:52.539 --> 10:54.280
this is a pretty big gig,
and it's about to start.

10:54.380 --> 10:55.661
Or did you forget?

10:55.761 --> 10:57.771
- I'm broke,
I'm soaked,

10:57.871 --> 10:59.382
I'm probably single,
and now I'm gonna have
to walk home.

10:59.482 --> 11:00.687
Is that what you're telling me?

11:00.787 --> 11:03.703
- Well, you know,
at least it's a nice night.

11:10.340 --> 11:12.081
- What is up, mi gente?

11:12.181 --> 11:17.183
I'm MC Cubano,
and let's get
this party started!

11:17.283 --> 11:19.984
All right, Deering High School.
Let's dance!

11:20.084 --> 11:22.132
- Kill me now.
- Pump it up!

11:22.232 --> 11:24.319
Pump it up!
Pump it up!

11:30.673 --> 11:32.030
- Slow down.
- Are you serious?
You want me to slow down?

11:32.130 --> 11:35.752
- Hey.
You want a ride?

11:35.852 --> 11:37.593
Come on.
It's the least I can do.

11:37.693 --> 11:39.895
After all,
I feel kind of responsible.

11:39.995 --> 11:42.105
I did tell you to get the soup.

11:43.947 --> 11:46.264
- No, the soup was good,
actually.
I'm taking some home.

11:46.364 --> 11:47.952
- Let me take you home.

11:48.052 --> 11:50.560
- Oh, here we go.
- I meant to his home.

11:50.660 --> 11:52.517
- Hamilton, are you serious?
I mean, come on.

11:52.617 --> 11:53.936
- What do you say?

11:54.036 --> 11:55.624
In ten seconds,
TMZ's gonna be all over us,

11:55.724 --> 11:58.732
so are you in or are you out?

12:08.807 --> 12:12.006
- So, Daniel,
this is Piper, my best friend,

12:12.106 --> 12:13.886
my stylist Zoe,

12:13.986 --> 12:17.876
and this rude man is my manager,
Lewis.

12:17.976 --> 12:21.712
Ladies, Daniel's
had a really hard night.

12:21.812 --> 12:24.014
I think we should cheer him up,
right?

12:24.114 --> 12:26.032
What do you wanna do?

12:26.646 --> 12:28.771
Anything.
Sky's the limit.
You wanna go somewhere?

12:28.871 --> 12:31.303
- How 'bout Bermuda?
- We just flew here.

12:31.403 --> 12:32.953
- You are so...
-  Stop!

12:33.053 --> 12:35.753
- I have to work in the morning.
- Relax, Cinderella.

12:35.853 --> 12:38.017
I'll have you home before
you turn into a pumpkin.

12:38.117 --> 12:41.585
What do you wanna do more than
anything in the whole world?

12:43.795 --> 12:45.958
- Change my shirt.
- Practical man.

12:46.058 --> 12:47.454
How refreshing.

12:47.554 --> 12:49.948
- Lewis, can I please
have your shirt?

12:50.048 --> 12:51.368
- Uh, I'm gonna have
to call you back.

12:51.468 --> 12:52.365
I beg your pardon?

12:52.465 --> 12:53.746
- I know that you're
wearing layers.

12:53.846 --> 12:54.782
- This is Gucci.

12:54.882 --> 12:57.429
- Please?
-  All right.

12:57.529 --> 12:59.884
If you ever question
how much I love you, Hamilton,

12:59.984 --> 13:02.340
I am going to remind you
of this moment.

13:02.440 --> 13:03.606
- I'm so grateful.

13:03.706 --> 13:05.754
- This is cashmere.

13:05.854 --> 13:07.327
- You're such a snob.

13:11.379 --> 13:13.043
- Is that making
you uncomfortable?
We can look away.

13:13.143 --> 13:15.384
Girls, look away.
- No, I'm gonna keep looking.

13:15.484 --> 13:17.455
- Wow.
- Keep your eyes on the road,
honestly.

13:17.555 --> 13:19.642
- Keep your eyes forward too.

13:19.742 --> 13:21.483
- Thank you.

13:21.583 --> 13:25.627
- Okay,
that was your first wish.
A shirt.

13:25.727 --> 13:29.924
Now, I'm gonna ask you what
you want for your second wish,
but before that,

13:30.024 --> 13:31.497
I really need your help
with something.

13:31.597 --> 13:34.681
- I'm almost afraid to ask.
- Oh, he catches on quick.

13:34.781 --> 13:38.901
- With what?
- My mustache.

13:44.410 --> 13:46.382
- Long time.
Good to see you.

13:46.482 --> 13:47.609
Long time.

13:47.709 --> 13:50.142
And this is my new friend,
Daniel.

13:50.242 --> 13:51.066
- Daniel.
- Daniel, nice to meet you.

14:17.940 --> 14:19.605
Nice.
- Never looked better.

14:23.772 --> 14:25.513
- Point of no return, brother.

14:28.376 --> 14:30.961
- Hey, can I get you anything?

14:31.061 --> 14:32.457
- You mean like a gun?

14:32.557 --> 14:34.299
One of those little
kitchen knives

14:34.399 --> 14:36.716
chefs use to dice up carrots
into tiny slices?

14:45.831 --> 14:49.453
Okay.

14:49.553 --> 14:51.678
Maybe I'm overreacting.

14:51.778 --> 14:55.361
In fairness, my proposal
was more sort of my thing
than his.

14:55.461 --> 14:57.279
I spooked him.

14:57.379 --> 14:58.890
Plus he's Cuban,
so he has that whole
macho thing.

14:58.990 --> 15:00.732
- Yes, yes, he does.

15:00.832 --> 15:04.415
- Maybe I overstepped
in depriving him
the chance to ask me?

15:04.515 --> 15:05.872
I mean, I know he loves me.

15:05.972 --> 15:07.522
He said he loved the idea
of the house.

15:07.622 --> 15:09.939
He even said he wanted me
to go dancing more,

15:10.039 --> 15:12.509
and everyone knows dancing
is just a metaphor for sex.

15:12.609 --> 15:16.192
- After four years
to still have all that passion,
that is incredible.

15:16.292 --> 15:18.034
- Right?

15:18.134 --> 15:20.758
Oh, I'm so dramatic,
aren't I?

15:20.858 --> 15:23.597
- The greats always are.
- Oh!

15:23.697 --> 15:25.438
Poor Daniel.

15:25.538 --> 15:29.006
He's probably curled up
somewhere scared to death
he's lost me forever.

15:32.827 --> 15:35.259
Hey. You doing okay?

15:35.359 --> 15:39.211
- Is this a typical night?
- Uh, with Noa,
there's no such thing.

15:39.311 --> 15:41.628
Well, it's her father's hotel,
and he used her image
without her approval,

15:41.728 --> 15:45.272
so we're turning it into
an image she does approve of.

15:45.372 --> 15:47.651
- That's right.
Come down.

15:53.237 --> 15:55.247
Are you happy you got
in the car?

15:55.347 --> 15:58.071
Ask me when I'm back on Earth.

15:59.299 --> 16:01.769
Should I worry that you feel
the need to deface yourself?

16:01.869 --> 16:03.189
- Should I worry
that when I told you

16:03.289 --> 16:04.761
you could do
anything you want,

16:04.861 --> 16:08.022
the best you could come up with
was change your shirt?

16:08.122 --> 16:10.194
- Yeah, but it is a nice shirt.

16:14.376 --> 16:17.115
- This is the Gordon hotel,
right?
- Yeah.

16:17.215 --> 16:20.261
- There's a wedding down there.
My family made the pastries
for it.

16:23.161 --> 16:26.130
- You're a baker?
- My dad has a place
in Little Havana.

16:26.230 --> 16:29.391
Rafael's,
but we all work there.

16:29.491 --> 16:31.540
- Who's we?

16:31.640 --> 16:34.532
- Me, my brother,
my sister,
and my parents.

16:34.632 --> 16:36.796
- Are you all close?

16:36.896 --> 16:39.941
- Sometimes maybe too close.
What about you?

16:46.141 --> 16:50.607
- Are you turning my mustache
into a butterfly?

16:50.707 --> 16:52.410
That's amazing.

16:54.236 --> 16:56.054
- I like to paint.

16:56.154 --> 16:58.740
- Full of surprises.

17:21.244 --> 17:23.163
- I know.

18:01.143 --> 18:03.614
- Aye, uh-oh.
Aye, Papa.

18:03.714 --> 18:05.532
That's the home phone.
It must be one of the kids.

18:05.632 --> 18:07.412
Hello?
Is everything all right?

18:07.512 --> 18:09.829
- Mari, it's Vanessa.

18:09.929 --> 18:12.246
I'm sorry to disturb you but I
was hoping to talk to Daniel.

18:12.346 --> 18:16.005
- Isn't he with you?
- No.

18:16.105 --> 18:19.880
So you haven't heard from him
about anything, then?

18:19.980 --> 18:21.185
- Why?
Is something wrong?

18:21.285 --> 18:22.144
- Que paso?
Baby, que paso?

18:22.244 --> 18:25.712
- No.
I

18:25.812 --> 18:28.282
I wasn't feeling well
so I asked him to take me home.

18:28.382 --> 18:30.584
I just wanted to let him know
my fever broke,
but his phone is off.

18:30.684 --> 18:32.602
Anyway, gotta go.
Bye.

18:35.441 --> 18:37.144
Get ready.

18:46.682 --> 18:48.960
- Um, you're
